<!--
    Sparkle update feed for Penova for Mac.
    Live at https://penova.pages.dev/appcast.xml — must match the
    SUFeedURL value in PenovaMac/App/Info.plist exactly.

    Each release adds an item block above the previous one
    (newest first). Generate the block by running
    tools/sign-update.sh on the notarized DMG, then update the
    enclosure URL to the real CDN path and paste it in. See
    tools/RELEASE.md for the cutting-a-release flow.

    The sparkle:edSignature attribute on the enclosure is what
    gates trust: the user's installed app refuses to install any
    update whose signature doesn't verify against SUPublicEDKey
    in its bundled Info.plist.
-->
